name: DeepLX Translator
description: Free DeepL translation API plugin, no authkey required.\n\
\n\
Update plan:\n\
  1. add settings\n\
  2. add custom api\n\
\n\
The server side of this project has been in github open source:\n\
https://github.com/guobao2333/DeepLX-Serverless\n\
Welcome click to Star~\n\
Since the server has been blocked by DeepL, the new version of the plugin has built-in direct access to DeepL service via your local network. If you can't get the translation, please adjust your own network environment to access deepl.com

